---
import "../styles/global.css";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | Innovate-X";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Effective Date: June 18, 2025</p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
      personal information when you register for our tech meetup and 3-day
      training event through this website.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We collect personal data such as your name, email address, and phone
      number when you register using our Google Form.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">
      2. How We Use Your Information
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Your information is used solely for the purpose of managing your event
      registration and communicating updates. We do not sell or share your data
      with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Data is collected via Google Forms and stored securely on Googleâ€™s
      servers. We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. Your Rights Under NDPR</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Under the Nigeria Data Protection Regulation (NDPR), you have the right to
      access, correct, or request deletion of your personal data. Contact us to
      exercise these rights.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We use Google Forms for data collection. Please review
      <a
        href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-blue-600 underline">Google&apos;s Privacy Policy</a
      > for more information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">
      If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at: <strong
        ><a href="mailto:olakadasamuel@gmail.com">olakadasamuel@gmail.com</a
        ></strong
      >.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
